00:13:38.693 --> 00:13:40.163
No, President Myung.

00:13:40.762 --> 00:13:43.032
Stop trying to defend yourself with this nonsense.

00:13:43.663 --> 00:13:45.732
If I wasn't my mom's daughter,

00:13:46.433 --> 00:13:48.362
