00:14:30.813 --> 00:14:34.982
Confess everything, and apologize sincerely.

00:14:36.482 --> 00:14:39.382
Then Si Hyun will feel less guilty,

00:14:40.723 --> 00:14:41.752
and I...

00:14:42.622 --> 00:14:44.223
