00:16:27.693 --> 00:16:29.732
I'm sorry. I didn't see you.

00:16:30.463 --> 00:16:32.762
Hello? Hold on.

00:16:39.272 --> 00:16:41.502
Can you move?

00:16:41.803 --> 00:16:44.272
